20Agreement)%20refers%20to%20optical%20toys.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDevice%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20means%20any%20device%20that%20can%20access%20the%20Service%20such%20as%20a%20computer%2C%20a%20cellphone%20or%20a%20digital%20tablet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EService%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20refers%20to%20the%20Website.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETerms%20and%20Conditions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20(also%20referred%20as%20%E2%80%9CTerms%E2%80%9D)%20mean%20these%20Terms%20and%20Conditions%20that%20form%20the%20entire%20agreement%20between%20You%20and%20the%20Company%20regarding%20the%20use%20of%20the%20Service.%20This%20Terms%20and%20Conditions%20agreement%20has%20been%20created%20with%20the%20help%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.termsfeed.com%2Fterms-conditions-generator%2F%22%3ETermsFeed%20Terms%20and%20Conditions%20Generator%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThird-party%20Social%20Media%20Service%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20means%20any%20services%20or%20content%20(including%20data%2C%20information%2C%20products%20or%20services)%20provided%20by%20a%20third-party%20that%20may%20be%20displayed%2C%20included%20or%20made%20available%20by%20the%20Service.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWebsite%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20refers%20to%20optical%20toys%2C%20accessible%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%22https%3A%2F%2Foptical.toys%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Foptical.toys%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EYou%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20means%20the%20individual%20accessing%20or%20using%20the%20Service%2C%20or%20the%20company%2C%20or%20other%20legal%20entity%20on%20behalf%20of%20which%20such%20individual%20is%20accessing%20or%20using%20the%20Service%2C%20as%20applicable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Ch1%20id%3D%22acknowledgment%22%3EAcknowledgment%3C%2Fh1%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20are%20the%20Terms%20and%20Conditions%20governing%20the%20use%20of%20this%20Service%20and%20the%20agreement%20that%20operates%20between%20Y